reviewText: This is a high quality DVD. We like it very much. Thank you.

A great video of Leon and the bluegrass band. A must-buy for all Leon fans.
His performance of A Song for You at the end is the best yet.
This is no a new grass DVD this is a Leon Russell DVD with a few new grass harmonies
Classic bluegrass with a fantastic performance of the master Len.
Very good a good Leon Russell
